        <h2 id="compensation-benchmarks">2026 Compensation Benchmarks</h2>

        <p>Competitive compensation is table stakes in today's market. Companies paying below-market rates report 34% higher turnover and 28% longer hiring cycles. Here are the current market rates by experience level and region.</p>

