        <h3>Building a Sustainable Management System</h3>

        <p>Create standard operating procedures for every aspect of employee management: recruiting, interviewing, onboarding, training, and performance management. Document best practices and update them quarterly based on results and feedback.</p>

        <p>Invest in supervisor training. Many technical experts lack people management skills. Consider external management training programs costing $2,500-5,000 per supervisor but yielding 25% better team performance.</p>

        <p>The most successful HVAC companies treat employee management as a core competency, not an HR afterthought. With the right systems, compensation strategies, and tools, you can build a team that drives profitable growth even in today's challenging labor market.</p>
